OL,4,G1200FCouples Come Dine with Me
OL,5,     GIn west London, Queen and Shawn
OL,6,     Gtake inspiration from their Thai
OL,7,     Gand West Indian heritage. Paul
OL,8,     Gand Suzy plan a fancy French
OL,9,     Gfeast. And Charlotte and Kevin
OL,10,     Gserve up Japanese cuisine.
OL,11,G1300FCouples Come Dine with Me
OL,12,     GOn the south coast, there are
OL,13,     Gexperimental flavour
OL,14,     Gcombinations, banjo playing and a
OL,15,     GBilly Connolly lookalike, as
OL,16,     Gthree rival couples put their
OL,17,     Ghosting skills to the test.
